<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
            habt, wie ew her Walthasar von Maspach, <expan>tümh<ex>e</ex>r</expan> czü
                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und probst czü Onelspach, fürbracht hab, daz Hans
            Topler und <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> Czingel, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, als vormünd <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Toplers
            seligen kind <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> probstey güte czü Insingen auf das
                <expan>lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan> des burggrafentüms
              <expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir die
                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> darumb besant und cze rede gesaczt und die
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns geantwurt, daz sie das <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
            der kinder <add>grosser</add> notdurft <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> getan
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und <expan>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz sie etliche
                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> kinde güte <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> not
                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>kauffen</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> müszen, die <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Walthasar, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> probst, <expan>cze
                leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geen, die er den, die sie gekawfft
              <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, bisher nicht <expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolt, wie
            wol sie das <expan>czeitlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an in braht und
              <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>fleizzikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Doch so <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir sie durch
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen daran geweiset, daz sie von
              <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan></add> ladung lassen
              <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleizze, daz ir
            durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Walthasar reden und in daran weisen wöllet, daz er sölich
            güter den, die sie gekawffet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, noch
                <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
